event_save
Disk World creator help
event_save

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
event_save -  Objects that need to make this room save such as containers in the room should generate a save event to make the room save its inventory.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void event_save(object thing)
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/room_save.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Objects that need to make this room save such as containers in the room
should generate a save event to make the room save its inventory.
eg. event(environment(this_object()), "save");

.EP

